      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, I'll check the total door-to-door time. The airport is a total disaster right now though, it feels like everything is just falling apart and nothing is working right. It's pure chaos. Why do you think it's so much harder to get simple things sorted when things start getting delayed like this?",
